1
00:00:01,660 --> 00:00:03,693
(Shibuya) I... I'm married...

2
00:00:03,693 --> 00:00:05,726
(Natsuno Chinami) Huh? (Ayo Noda) Recent Chinami➡

3
00:00:05,726 --> 00:00:10,000
That's strange. Neglect yourself➡

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,066
It's like anyone can fill in the empty hole.

5
00:00:12,066 --> 00:00:14,759
Even Ayase doesn't understand my feelings!

6
00:00:14,759 --> 00:00:18,297
sorry…. I don't want to try it anymore.

7
00:00:18,297 --> 00:00:22,099
I think it's wrong. Who is using Murata?

8
00:00:22,099 --> 00:00:24,132
Thank you so far.

9
00:00:24,132 --> 00:00:27,858
♬〜

10
00:00:27,858 --> 00:00:29,891
(Mikaru Umaji) Well then, let's buy some alcohol and go home. Yeah.

11
00:00:31,297 --> 00:00:33,330
Huh?

12
00:00:37,198 --> 00:00:40,891
Ssssssssssss...(footsteps)

13
00:00:40,891 --> 00:00:43,165
It's cold. (Shibuya) Haha yes.

14
00:00:43,165 --> 00:00:46,000
already~. thank you.

15
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:48,033
Yeah. Push (sound of opening a can)

16
00:00:52,495 --> 00:00:54,528
What were you watching?

17
00:00:56,198 --> 00:00:59,528
I want to see this movie. yeah?

18
00:00:59,528 --> 00:01:01,957
It's the weekend together...

19
00:01:05,759 --> 00:01:10,231
On the weekends... it's not good.

20
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:33,033
(Shibuya) Sorry.

21
00:01:40,297 --> 00:01:42,330
(Shibuya) Sorry...

22
00:01:49,000 --> 00:02:09,000
♬〜

23
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:29,000
♬〜

24
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:32,000
♬〜

25
00:02:34,462 --> 00:02:36,825
Rattling…(keyboard operation sound)

26
00:02:45,297 --> 00:02:49,033
(Murata, recollection) ⦅But this is love...➡

27
00:02:49,033 --> 00:02:51,066
Everyone looks like they're heartbroken⦆

28
00:02:56,165 --> 00:02:58,429
(Hanai) Mr. Konno, I'm sorry. ➡

29
00:02:58,429 --> 00:03:00,693
Mr. Murata is on sick leave today. Meeting➡

30
00:03:00,693 --> 00:03:04,528
Is it okay if it's just me? (Konno) Murata? ➡

31
00:03:04,528 --> 00:03:07,891
rare…. (Hanai) It feels like a telephone➡

32
00:03:07,891 --> 00:03:10,297
Her voice also sounded quite painful due to the gas.

33
00:03:10,297 --> 00:03:12,462
(Konno) Eh, I guess it's okay.

34
00:03:18,726 --> 00:03:23,363
Eh, why me? (Konno) Well, I mean... hey?

35
00:03:25,033 --> 00:03:27,066
Ah...

36
00:03:29,429 --> 00:03:32,495
(Konno) Do you want to go to the meeting? (Hanai) That's right.

37
00:03:32,495 --> 00:03:52,297
♬〜

38
00:03:52,297 --> 00:03:54,330
📱(Message reception/Silent mode)

39
00:03:56,627 --> 00:03:59,165
Huh?

40
00:03:59,165 --> 00:04:02,330
｢２２２｣｢２２３｣｢２２４｣…。

41
00:04:02,330 --> 00:04:04,363
Hahaha….

42
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:09,627
Sigh… “225”! Rattle rattle! (door sound)

43
00:04:09,627 --> 00:04:13,198
Hehe, yes, come this way. No, don't take the picture.

44
00:04:13,198 --> 00:04:15,825
Stop it... Ah Ayase.

45
00:04:15,825 --> 00:04:17,858
Hey, isn't this light really a comedy?

46
00:04:17,858 --> 00:04:21,231
Don't laugh. Already... I think so too.

47
00:04:23,363 --> 00:04:25,660
What?!

48
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:27,693
Ayase, what happened?

49
00:04:29,099 --> 00:04:31,561
I was worried...

50
00:04:31,561 --> 00:04:34,495
There's nothing to cry about. Sorry.

51
00:04:36,792 --> 00:04:39,825
Wha... why did you get hurt?

52
00:04:39,825 --> 00:04:42,594
I fell down the stairs.

53
00:04:42,594 --> 00:04:45,759
Where? of the bar.

54
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:50,759
I drank a little too much. Why did you drink too much?

55
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:54,231
When it comes to land, I feel like I'm a bit of an alcoholic...

56
00:04:56,264 --> 00:04:58,429
What is it?

57
00:05:01,627 --> 00:05:04,726
Zu… (Sound of slurping) What are you guys?

58
00:05:10,231 --> 00:05:14,660
Always thinking about love➡

59
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:19,396
I'm always happy and worried about the other person, and I'm being tossed around like an idiot...

60
00:05:19,396 --> 00:05:23,066
Ayase... Why...➡

61
00:05:23,066 --> 00:05:26,066
Can't you live alone?

62
00:05:28,099 --> 00:05:32,627
Why do I have to be liked by someone?

63
00:05:32,627 --> 00:05:37,825
Why... why can't I just stay lonely?

64
00:05:40,726 --> 00:05:42,858
Me too.

65
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:50,033
To fill the empty hole➡

66
00:05:50,033 --> 00:05:54,165
Always pretending➡

67
00:05:54,165 --> 00:05:57,693
Always pretend like it's okay➡

68
00:05:57,693 --> 00:06:00,693
I've been cheating for a long time.

69
00:06:05,594 --> 00:06:07,627
But I don't like it anymore.

70
00:06:07,627 --> 00:06:17,264
♬〜

71
00:06:17,264 --> 00:06:19,297
I….

72
00:06:21,627 --> 00:06:23,891
I like light.

73
00:06:26,495 --> 00:06:30,594
Ever since I was a freshman in college.

74
00:06:30,594 --> 00:06:33,033
Even after finding out that Hikari is gay➡

75
00:06:33,033 --> 00:06:35,594
I couldn't stop the feeling of love.

76
00:06:35,594 --> 00:06:39,891
♬〜

77
00:06:39,891 --> 00:06:44,297
But now... I want to end it.

78
00:06:47,462 --> 00:06:49,495
I want to move forward.

79
00:06:52,561 --> 00:06:57,627
That's why I want you to say it. You don't like me.

80
00:07:01,429 --> 00:07:05,330
I want you to say it right from the light's mouth.

81
00:07:05,330 --> 00:07:25,165
♬〜

82
00:07:25,165 --> 00:07:30,429
The fact that Ayase used to like me is➡

83
00:07:30,429 --> 00:07:33,660
I knew it somehow.

84
00:07:33,660 --> 00:07:37,594
I'm sorry if I've made Ayase suffer for a long time because of that.

85
00:07:40,264 --> 00:07:43,825
But I am➡

86
00:07:43,825 --> 00:07:48,660
I can't say I don't like Ayase.

87
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:51,495
I am Ayase...➡

88
00:07:51,495 --> 00:07:54,891
Things that are clear➡

89
00:07:54,891 --> 00:07:58,759
Bad words, sarcasm, etc.➡

90
00:07:58,759 --> 00:08:02,660
I love that kind of thing.

91
00:08:02,660 --> 00:08:05,759
Because behind that is Ayase's love.

92
00:08:09,528 --> 00:08:13,132
It's not love though...➡

93
00:08:13,132 --> 00:08:15,165
Because I like Ayase.

94
00:08:17,891 --> 00:08:21,000
That Ayase has always loved me➡

95
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,198
I'm so happy➡

96
00:08:23,198 --> 00:08:25,825
I think you can live with just that feeling.

97
00:08:25,825 --> 00:08:36,891
♬〜

98
00:08:36,891 --> 00:08:41,627
Doodle... Do you remember?

99
00:08:41,627 --> 00:08:44,495
graffiti?

100
00:08:44,495 --> 00:08:48,099
I was sleeping in a university classroom...

101
00:08:48,099 --> 00:08:50,297
Ahaha, isn't that so?

102
00:08:50,297 --> 00:08:52,792
Ayase is drooling in her sleep.

103
00:08:52,792 --> 00:08:55,891
Fufufu…. Hehe.

104
00:08:55,891 --> 00:08:59,165
I remember. There's no way I'll forget.

105
00:08:59,165 --> 00:09:04,066
♬〜

106
00:09:04,066 --> 00:09:06,099
thank you.

107
00:09:06,099 --> 00:09:12,462
♬〜

108
00:09:13,825 --> 00:09:17,297
Boo! (Sound of chewing flowers) Hehe.

109
00:09:17,297 --> 00:09:20,132
Like a child. It's so noisy.

110
00:09:30,231 --> 00:09:33,693
yeah? what up?

111
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:43,033
Huh! Huh? what?

112
00:09:43,033 --> 00:09:46,198
Let go! Let me go.

113
