Hey... I thought you wouldn't notice?

114
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:54,660
What? My eyes... are swollen.

115
00:09:59,924 --> 00:10:04,594
I care about you too.

116
00:10:08,429 --> 00:10:13,231
That's why I don't want you to get hurt...

117
00:10:15,099 --> 00:10:17,132
I don't want you to cry.

118
00:10:19,099 --> 00:10:23,825
Take care of yourself and be happy.

119
00:10:23,825 --> 00:10:32,363
♬〜

120
00:10:32,363 --> 00:10:34,396
Yeah.

121
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:40,627
thank you. (2 people) Hehehe.

122
00:10:40,627 --> 00:10:43,660
⚟Shower sound...(Shower sound)

123
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:58,000
♬〜

124
00:11:15,660 --> 00:11:19,528
I was fine alone. It must be lonely being discharged from the hospital alone.

125
00:11:19,528 --> 00:11:21,726
Actually, Ayyo wanted to come too.

126
00:11:21,726 --> 00:11:23,759
Am I a child?

127
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:26,462
Please sit down while I make you some coffee. Okay, I'll do it.

128
00:11:26,462 --> 00:11:30,066
That's fine already. You've never ground beans, have you?

129
00:11:30,066 --> 00:11:32,429
There's no way that's the case. Hehehe.

130
00:11:32,429 --> 00:11:34,462
thank you. Yeah.

131
00:11:34,462 --> 00:11:39,825
Jar...(sound of water being poured into a kettle)

132
00:11:39,825 --> 00:11:41,858
Good...

133
00:11:43,231 --> 00:11:45,957
Click, click, click... (sound of stove) Are you grinding it from the beans every time?

134
00:11:45,957 --> 00:11:48,000
Fashionable.

135
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:51,033
Lately, Riku has been doing everything for me.

136
00:11:54,132 --> 00:11:56,165
Clicking... (sound of beans being added to coffee milk)

137
00:11:59,627 --> 00:12:03,000
Grinding... (sound of grinding beans)

138
00:12:04,924 --> 00:12:07,792
It’s me…➡

139
00:12:07,792 --> 00:12:12,561
