246
00:22:22,759 --> 00:22:25,561
But I'm glad. Yes... that's right.

247
00:22:27,858 --> 00:22:29,891
Chinami's turn. Yeah.

248
00:22:32,990 --> 00:22:36,066
Sigh, it's not good anymore.

249
00:22:36,066 --> 00:22:38,759
Love is over. (3 people) Hehe.

250
00:22:41,330 --> 00:22:44,561
Oh, new development? Hehe.

251
00:22:44,561 --> 00:22:46,594
oh~. Ahaha.

252
00:22:46,594 --> 00:22:50,363
Hehe. Hehe.

253
00:22:50,363 --> 00:22:53,165
Come to think of it, how much Karuta is left?

254
00:22:53,165 --> 00:22:57,066
Just “n”. “Hmm” huh?

255
00:22:57,066 --> 00:22:59,099
Yeah….

256
00:23:03,023 --> 00:23:06,198
Hmm...➡

257
00:23:06,198 --> 00:23:09,429
Well, I liked it.

258
00:23:11,825 --> 00:23:13,858
Fufufu….

259
00:23:13,858 --> 00:23:19,627
♬〜

260
00:23:19,627 --> 00:23:21,660
Good.

261
00:23:23,429 --> 00:23:27,561
I'll take it then.

262
00:23:27,561 --> 00:23:29,594
Write it.

263
00:23:31,561 --> 00:23:34,066
Eh, then it's completed? Karuta.

264
00:23:34,066 --> 00:23:38,594
That's right. Huh! Yay!

265
00:23:38,594 --> 00:23:40,627
Let's have a toast. Cheers. Yay!

266
00:23:40,627 --> 00:23:43,891
Hey. Good luck! thank you~.

267
00:23:43,891 --> 00:23:45,990
